 enough to give it a recommend. I bought it on sale for $1.24 and have no regrets.\n\nAlso, the game played well for me on Linux Mint 18 (Wine/PlayOnLinux). The one minor issue I experienced was that once I had initially configured the game to display in Fullscreen in the game's Options, the first time I'd click Play in a given session, it would start in window mode. I would then have to exit via the game's Menu and hit Play again to get it to play as expected in borderless fullscreen. Other than that, I experience no issues.\n\nPS I almost exclusively play offline. I typically only play online long enough for Steam to allow me to write a review. So Steam only shows that I played 0.5 hrs as of the time of this review, although I've played at least 3 hrs and have completed the game.\n\nUpdate: Added 'difficulty settings' portion.", "timestamp_updated": 1486843884, "written_during_early_access": false, "comment_count": 0, "received_for_free": false, "timestamp_created": 1486800144, "votes_down": 0}, {"recommendationid": "20609893", "steam_purchase": true, "votes_up": 1, "weighted_vote_score": "0.500111", "voted_up": true, "language": "english", "author": {"last_played": 1453141824, "steamid": "76561198257572602", "num_games_owned": 259, "num_reviews": 16, "playtime_forever": 237, "playtime_last_two_weeks": 0}, "votes_funny": 0, "review": "Great game.  I enjoyed playing it.  Lots of HOGs and puzzles.  Some harder than others but all doable.  I give it a 7 out of 10.", "timestamp_updated": 1453141918, "written_during_early_access": false, "comment_count": 0, "received_for_free": false, "timestamp_created": 1453141918, "votes_down": 0}, {"recommendationid": "21141188", "steam_purchase": true, "votes_up": 1, "weighted_vote_score": "0.500111", "voted_up": true, "language": "english", "author": {"last_played": 1455219584, "steamid": "76561198030663271", "num_games_owned": 116, "num_reviews": 9, "playtime_forever": 184, "playtime_last_two_weeks": 0}, "votes_funny": 0, "revie